The staff is extremely friendly, very helpful and most spoke good English.	The bathroom was spacious and clean too.	The room was very clean and surprisingly spacious enough to accomodate the 3 of us and our luggages.	The front desk was very polite and helpful.	The included breakfast was good.	Staff were pleasant, friendly and helpful.	Breakfast was typical for Rome hotels, basic but more than adequate.	We would recommend this hotel and would definitely stay there again.	The hotel was close to Termini as we arrived by train.